This Act contains provisions on:
* purpose, contents, and definitions of the Act (Chapter 1);
* public and private interests (Chapter 2);
* the comprehensive plan (Chapter 3);
* regulations with detailed development plan and area regulations (Chapter 4);
* procedures for detailed development plans and area regulations (Chapter 5);
* the implementation of detailed development plans (Chapter 6);
* regional planning (Chapter 7);
* requirements for construction works, construction products, lots, and public
* building permits, demolition permits and site improvement permits, etc.
